  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/fa09f23c2df0d5300aa9f6a6591cf251.poster.avif?t=1701573279\" width=615 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/fa09f23c2df0d5300aa9f6a6591cf251.webm?t=1701573279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>           This is an <strong>hardcore arcade-style</strong> game with a focus on fast and skill-based gameplay and immersive audiovisuals. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>           It relies on a simple, intuitive control scheme that allows players to quickly grasp the mechanics.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/6548c28167e6b97c9a4f770eb2a8797b.poster.avif?t=1701573279\" width=614 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/6548c28167e6b97c9a4f770eb2a8797b.webm?t=1701573279\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/6548c28167e6b97c9a4f770eb2a8797b.mp4?t=1701573279\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The game has a series of increasingly challenging levels that require the player to use their reflexes and timing to overcome obstacles. Gameplay of the game is <strong>highly addictive</strong>, as players strive to improve their <strong>skills</strong> and beat their <strong>high scores</strong>. The game features an immersive soundtrack and exellent graphic design<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283360/extras/62bb24984f168a74802adf5081121ce9.avif?t=1701573279\" width=615 height=243 /></span>",
